[This message came via Merritt Clifton, editor of 'Animal People', who
commented: "I have many contacts in the Visakhapatnam area, near where the
anthrax outbreaks are occurring. I forwarded your posting to them, and
received back the following from Pradeep Kumar Nath, founder of the Visakha
SPCA (now one of the largest in India):" So I think we can assume that the
situation is as bad as it appears to be. Merritt -- Many thanks. - Mod.MHJ]

